{"arkId":"cl010113428","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010113428","modified ":"2026-03-11","title":"Manteau d\u0027officier de l\u0027Ordre du Saint-Esprit","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Manteau d\u0027officier de l\u0027Ordre du Saint-Esprit"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Philippe d\u0027Orl\u00e9ans (1715-1723) (Occident-\u003E\u00e9poque moderne = Ancien R\u00e9gime-\u003Edynastie des Bourbons) ; Louis XV (1715-1774) (Occident-\u003E\u00e9poque moderne = Ancien R\u00e9gime-\u003Edynastie des Bourbons)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : vers 1722 (ancienne datation XVIIe si\u00e8cle) (source documentaire ou archivistique)","currentLocation":"Richelieu, [OArt] Salle 523 - Salle de l\u0027ordre du Saint-Esprit","room":"Salle 523, Aile Aile Richelieu, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1722,"endYear":"","imprecision":"vers","text":"1er quart du XVIIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Anonyme","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"Brodeur","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q4233718"}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"MS 54","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"},{"value":"CL 18559","type":"Autre num\u00e9ro d\u0027inventaire"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"textile divers ; manteau de c\u00e9r\u00e9monie","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Manteau d\u0027officier de l\u0027ordre du Saint-Esprit en velours de soie noir, brod\u00e9 d\u0027un semis de 478 flammes d\u0027or et d\u0027argent sur toute la surface. Une plaque d\u0027argent repr\u00e9sentant une colombe est brod\u00e9e sur la face du manteau. Le manteau des quatre officiers qui administraient l\u0027Ordre (pr\u00e9v\u00f4t ma\u00eetre des c\u00e9r\u00e9monies, grand tr\u00e9sorier, greffier-secr\u00e9taire, h\u00e9raut) \u00e9tait semblable \u00e0 celui des chevaliers mais n\u0027\u00e9tait pas brod\u00e9 du motif du collier de l\u0027ordre sur sa bordure.\r\nLa partie sup\u00e9rieure est recouverte d\u0027un grand col ou mantelet (ou \u00e9pitoge) de toile d\u0027argent verte, brod\u00e9e des m\u00eames motifs. L\u0027ensemble \u00e9tait doubl\u00e9 de satin jaune orang\u00e9.\r\nLe manteau est de forme ovo\u00efdale avec un effet de tra\u00eene.","inscriptions":"","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"139","displayDimension":"139 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Longueur","value":"415","displayDimension":"415 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"290","displayDimension":"290 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":5,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau\/Technique : Velours de soie brod\u00e9 de fils m\u00e9talliques\r\nTechnique : techniques textile\r\nTechnique : velours (techniques textile-\u003Etissu uni) (de soie)\r\nCouleur : noir = noire\r\nTechnique : fil m\u00e9tallique (techniques textile-\u003Efil)\r\nMat\u00e9riau : argent\r\nMat\u00e9riau : or","placeOfCreation":"Paris (France-\u003EIle-de-France = Ile de France)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Trianon ; Mus\u00e9e des Souverains","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[],"acquisitionDetails":[],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"period":[{"value":"Louis XV (1715-1774)"},{"value":"Philippe d\u0027Orl\u00e9ans (1715-1723)"}],"place":[{"value":"Paris"}],"